[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "美術品収集家",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "命を救っていただき、本当にありがとうございました。\nお礼に、この「九偉人図」をお譲りします",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとう！　助かるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あの……他の「九偉人図」の在り処について、\n心当たりはありませんか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "美術品収集家",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "申し訳ありません。\n他の「九偉人図」については、私も何も……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "美術品収集家",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "とはいえ、希少な美術品です。\n私のような人を訪ねれば、いずれ見つかるでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "となると、これからは無数島群域中の美術品収集家を\n地道に回るしかなさそうだね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "まあ、地道な調査も嫌いじゃないさ。\n美術品の話なら僕も興味あるしね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ、みんなで協力して集めていきましょ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……警告。再び町に胞子が飛来。あのキノコの特性を\n引き継ぐ個体が、すでに育ち始めている模様",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "またかよ……しつこいキノコだねぇ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "まだ胞子の散布が始まったばかりなら、\n被害は防げるはず！　魔物を倒しに行こう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうね。みんなで向かうわよ！\n今度こそ、根絶やしにしてやるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "任せときな、相棒！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "みんなで町を守ろう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……ヴァレリア姉ちゃんには、信頼できる友達が\nたくさんいるんだね。羨ましいな……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私も、そんな風になれたらいいのに……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……キューン、あなたにも、きっとできる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……うん。ありがとう、ヤド姉",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]